AMENDEDANALYSIS
Thisbill:
I. Requiresahealthcarefacilitytoprovidecertified,writtennoticetoacriticalaccesshospitalif
thefacilitywillbelocatedwithina15mileradiusofthecriticalaccesshospital.
II. Establishes standards governing the transfer of patients from freestanding hospital
emergency facilities to acute care hospitals to ensure that such transfers are based primarily on
clinicalappropriateness,patientsafety,continuityofcare,andpatientchoice.
III. Bans coercive or exclusive transfer practices, reinforces EMTALA requirements, and gives
thestateauthoritytoenforceviolations.
